replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"個女比人打到咁都可以唔理，都老豆都唔會好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac834c3833ed3b1c75b897c971d02be85d4eee04","tid":709851,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"957af89796c1fb14fde2578951fa3b44d946e14e","tid":709851,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"另一單新聞講過<br />\n個女其實都唔係條仔親生"}]}